      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING HOPKINS (4) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 29.62 beating Back Tomorrow. The form from his last run stacks up well. Form reads well for this. SAMMY ETHAN (1) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd over 520m at this track beaten a neck (29.78) behind BOTH BOWERS ACE in a Mix 2/3 on February 19. Bold showing expected. BOTH BOWERS ACE (5) shapes well for this after winning last start over the 520m at this track in a brilliant 29.76. Should be in this for a long way. PLAYER ONE (8) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
